in your public_html folder do the following:

for each file (user_functions.php, connection.php):

chmod 700 <file>
setfacl -m mask:rwx <file>
setfacl -m user:blackc6:rwx <file>
setfacl -m user:carlind0:rwx <file>
setfacl -m user:pierosn0:rwx <file>
setfacl -m user:kilroy:rwx <file>
setfacl -m user:apache:rwx <file>

chmod 664 <file>

test to make sure that everything still works
